data.description: Backyard Oasis with Pool and Spa, outdoor kitchen, large covered patio and huge yard to entertain! This spacious home features a Game-room, Media Room, 4 bedrooms and 2.1 bathrooms in the highly sought after Gated community of Lake Ridge located in Cedar Hill. A one of a kind open floor plan that features a ton of natural light throughout anyone would love. As you enter the open entry you have a grand spiral staircase, dining room and office. A large gourmet kitchen with granite counters, electric cooktop, stainless steel appliances & large island that opens to the family room with fireplace. Beautiful views of the pool and backyard can be seen from the family room! The primary suite downstairs has a spa like bathroom with a separate tub and shower with a custom walk-in closet with built in cabinets. Upstairs you'll find three bedrooms and a full-bath game room, and a theater room.Minutes from Joe Pool lake and Tangle Ridge Golf Course.
